SUMMARY:Liberty by the Bay
LOCATION:1001 N Blvd Tampa \, FL 33607 United States
DESCRIPTION:The City of Tampa is celebrating Americas 250th anniversary wi
 th one of the largest Fourth of July events in Tampa Bay  Liberty by the B
 ay at Julian B. Lane Park (https:www.tampa.govparks-and-recreationfeatured
 -parksriverfrontpark). This free\, family-friendly waterfront celebration 
 will feature a 250-drone light show honoring Americas 250th birthday\, fol
 lowed by a fireworks finale\, along with an afternoon and evening full of 
 activities\, live entertainment\, food\, and fun for all ages. Learn more 
 at tampa.govlibertybythebay (https:www.tampa.govlibertybythebay) \n\nPerma
 link: https://www.tampa.gov/node/191651
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/191651
