SUMMARY:3rd Annual Tampa Tech Show
LOCATION:Hanna Avenue Municipal Building 2555 East Hanna Avenue Tampa \, F
 L 33610 United States
DESCRIPTION:Step into the future of innovation Experience firsthand how te
 chnology is transforming the way we live\, work\, and play at our Technolo
 gy Innovation Departments third annual Tampa Tech Show on Friday\, July 10
 \, from 10 a.m. to 3 p.m. at the City Center at Hanna Avenue (2555 East Ha
 nna Avenue). Explore interactive exhibits\, discover emerging technologies
 \, and watch live demonstrations while connecting with local innovators\, 
 entrepreneurs\, educators and technology leaders. Whether youre a student\
 , small business owner\, tech enthusiast or simply interested in whats nex
 t\, the Tampa Tech Show is the place to be. Stop by during lunch to suppor
 t local food trucks from 11 a.m. to 2 p.m. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tamp
 a.gov/node/192606
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/192606
