DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Tampas 139th birthday by learning more about its his
 tory. Tampa Bay History Center historians Rodney Kite-Powell and Fred Hear
 ns will talk about two historical events that happened 100 years ago. Lear
 n about the creation of Black History Month\, as well as the mysterious de
 ath of Davis Islands founder D.P. Davis. Birthday cake will be served foll
 owing the program. Guests will receive a commemorative booklet: 100 Years 
