SUMMARY:The Tampa General Hospital Heritage Archive
LOCATION:N/A Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:The Library Services team at Tampa General Hospital is buildin
 g a heritage archives program from the ground up  led by librarians having
  no prior archival infrastructure in place  to capture nearly a century of
  institutional history. From organizing an archival governance council mad
 e up of long-term employees\, physicians and hospital leaders to developin
 g collection workflows and gathering submissions\, this project showcases 
 how library professionals can champion archival preservation\, turning sca
 ttered institutional memory into a lasting\, accessible record of medical 
 milestones\, community impact\, and organizational identity. Please note\,
