  when you need to seek out professional help and practical exercises you c
 an start using right away. Whether youre curious\, dealing with symptoms\,
  or just want to feel stronger and more confident in your body\, this talk
  will give you the knowledge and tools to take control of your pelvic heal
 th. July 15\, 2026 Julie Blacker DPT 12-12:45 pm Register Here (https:even
