SUMMARY:Mayor039\\\;s Neighborhood University Saturday Session - Software 
 Saturday
LOCATION:2555 East Hanna Avenue Tampa \, FL 33610 United States
DESCRIPTION:Software Saturday July 25 from 9 am - 12 pm Hanna Avenue City 
 Center\, 2555 East Hanna Avenue Technology is changing the way we work\, c
 ommunicate\, and connect with our communities. Whether youre looking to st
 rengthen your online presence\, sharpen your digital skills\, or learn abo
 ut todays most useful tools\, this Mayors Neighborhood University Saturday
  Session is for you. Join City of Tampa interns and the Technology Innovat
 ion Team for an interactive morning exploring practical digital skills you
  can use every day. Participants will learn how to protect their privacy o
 nline\, build a personal brand\, stay connected with City government throu
 gh digital tools\, use artificial intelligence responsibly\, and create si
 mple flyers using Canva and Adobe Express. Whether youre a student\, neigh
 borhood leader\, nonprofit volunteer\, small business owner\, or simply in
 terested in learning something new\, youll leave with practical tips and r
 esources to help you navigate todays digital world with confidence. \n\nPe
 rmalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/192651
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/192651
END:VEVENT
