SUMMARY:Ava Rice The Eighth Sin
LOCATION:1731 East 7th Avenue Tampa \, FL 33605 United States
DESCRIPTION:Deep in the Underworld\, seven Sin Accountants (one for each o
 f the Seven Deadly Sins) are struggling to meet their quotas: humanity is 
 simply too used to sin. Thats when a determined rookie named Avarice heads
  to the Human World to identify a new\, eighth sin and save her job in the
  process. But what she uncovers doesnt just break the rules: it threatens 
 the fate of humanity itself! From writer Pedro Amaral comes a wickedly fun
 ny new musical that dives headfirst into sin\, chaos\, and the flaws that 
 make us human. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/191916
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/191916
END:VEVENT
