SUMMARY:Charter Review Commission Meeting
LOCATION:Tampa Old City Hall - Sister Cities Room 315 East Kennedy Bouleva
 rd Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:CHARTER REVIEW ADVISORY COMMISSION MEETING Date: Tuesday\, Aug
 ust 11\, 2026 Time: 6:00pm to 9:00pm Location: Old City Hall  Sister Citie
 s Room 315 East Kennedy Boulevard Tampa\, Florida 33602 Facilitator Robert
  Hendrickson will facilitate meetings of the 2025 Charter Review Advisory 
 Commission. The commissions purpose is to review the Tampa Home Rule Chart
 er of 1975\, as amended\, and propose any amendments or revisions by major
 ity vote of the Commission\, and present a report with their recommendatio
 ns to City Council\, which may by two-thirds vote of City Council be place
 d on the ballot for a vote on March 2\, 2027. Meetings are scheduled month
 ly for the 2 nd and 4 th Tuesday. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/nod
 e/180091
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/180091
