SUMMARY:Pride Passion: 20th Anniversay
LOCATION:120 W. Gasparilla Plaza Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate 20 Years of Pride Passion at the Tampa Museum of Art
 \, an event where myths come alive! On Saturday\, September 19\, 2026\, Pr
 ide Passion: Go Greek and Roman transforms the Museum into a playful tribu
 te to the Tampa Museum of Arts iconic collection of Greek and Roman antiqu
 ities\, bringing the drama and larger-than-life stories of mythology into 
 the spotlight! Adorn yourself in drapery\, armor\, or glamour as you embod
 y gods\, goddesses\, heroes\, and muses. Sip like Dionysus at our open bar
 \, indulge in delectable hors doeuvres from local LGBTQ friendly vendors\,
  and experience captivating performances inspired by the drama and romance
  of classical mythology. The evening promises enchantment\, intrigue\, and
  unforgettable celebration. Proceeds from Pride Passion directly support t
 he Museums Artful Connections program \, which uses art to foster healing\
 , creativity\, and connection for individuals navigating mental health cha
 llenges\, trauma or other health or emotional concerns. By attending or sp
 onsoring this beloved fundraiser\, you help us build an inclusive\, vibran
 t community through the power of art. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov
 /node/191546
