DESCRIPTION:The NAMIWalks Hillsborough will take place on Saturday\, Octob
 er 24\, 2026\, at Rowlett Park from 11:00 a.m.  2:00 p.m. ET. Registration
  opens at 10:00 a.m.\, the Opening Ceremony begins at 11:00 a.m.\, and the
  walk officially starts at 11:20 a.m. Hosted by NAMI Hillsborough\, this a
 nnual community walk brings together individuals\, families\, organization
 s\, and community leaders to raise awareness about mental health\, reduce 
 stigma\, and advocate for those impacted by mental health conditions. NAMI
 Walks is more than a walk. It is a movement of hope\, healing\, education\
 , and community connection. We walk to remind individuals and families the
 y are not alone\, to honor those impacted by mental health challenges\, an
 d to help expand access to free mental health education\, support groups\,
  and community resources throughout Hillsborough County. \n\nPermalink: ht
