  of every month from 11am to 2pm. Join us for truckloads of local favorite
 s and food that goes the extra mile. (Literally!) Thank you to the City of
  Tampa for their sponsorship of this event. (Interested in becoming a vend
 or? Contact Tampa Downtown Partnership!) - - - - - - - - - - Vmonos de fie
 sta! Debido a su popularidad (y hambre)\, el Mayors Food Truck Fiesta va a
