SUMMARY:Blind Date with a Book
LOCATION:W Kennedy Blvd &amp\; W Grand Central Ave Tampa \, FL 33602 Unite
 d States
DESCRIPTION:Its a match! Swipe right on a good read and start a new chapte
 r together during Blind Date with a Book. Each novel has page-turner poten
 tial but is wrapped to hide the cover  its bound to be good! Join us to un
 wrap a new favorite and experience love at first page. This event happens 
 four times a year\, so its the perfect opportunity to stay booked and busy
 ! WHEN: November 9  4:30-7:30pm WHERE: Snow Park We are partnering with Ox
 ford Exchange and TeBella Tea Company on this program. In addition\, huge 
 thank you to our sponsordonor the Hillsborough Public Library (Seminole He
 ights Location) for their help with this program. El amor est en el aire! 
 Comienza tu nueva historia de amor con nuestra Cita a Ciegas Con Un Libro.
  Cada obra viene envuelta y ocultando su portada. La idea es que el libro 
 que escojas sea una sorpresa! Acompanos para descubrir tu nueva aventura (
 y quin sabe? tal vez un amor a primera pgina). El evento es cuatro veces a
 l ao\, as que es la oportunidad perfecta para mantenerte ocupado! CUANDO: 
 9 de noviembre  4:30-7:30pm DONDE: Parque Snow \n\nPermalink: https://www.
 tampa.gov/node/188216
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/188216
END:VEVENT
